title: Pluginguru Omniverse for Omnisphere-6581 [deepstatus][h33t]
description:
Pluginguru Omniverse for Omnisphere





New Worlds for YOU to explore!

Omniverse packs a serious PUNCH for anybody that loves Omnisphere and wants new inspiring patches....

PlugInGuru is very happy to release a new library with 150 new places to explore in Omnisphere - from Thundering Deep Basses to the Most Sad and Lonley Piano Patch to over 50 bubbling pulsing Rhythmic patches. These are patches that will help you push the boundries of YOUR MUSIC into completely new dimensions...

The library is called Omniverse because of its versatility:

   this isn't just for DubSteppers (but there are wobble basses and radical sweeps and crazy leads)
   or for HipHoppers (but there are fat Sine Wave basses, leads and some ÃƒÂ¼ber-LUSH pads)
   or for Film buffs (but their are beautiful string patches, the Most Sad Ambient Piano and tons of beautiful BPM sync'd pads)

The patches are there for you to make your OWN world - and with the amazing range of sounds Omnisphere can create, the saying "the world is your oyster" just became a lot more applicable!

On top of the 150 patches, we added two additional sets of custom presets which can GREATLY expand the way you use of Omnisphere:

   The Envelope Preset Folder gives you 50 presets that can easily be applied to ANY Omnisphere patch to turn it into a BPM Sync'd rhythmic patch!

   The Arpeggiator Preset Folder will give you 40 Arpeggiator templates aimed at taking Omnisphere deeper into exciting worlds of Rhythmic maythem!

                 Macintosh
